    <ToastProvider>
      <AnchoredToastProvider>
        <EventRouter />
        <DesktopProjectBootstrap />
        <Outlet />
      </AnchoredToastProvider>
    </ToastProvider>
  );

  return <ThemeProvider>{inner}</ThemeProvider>;
}
```

Both approaches are correct. The ternary approach is marginally cleaner since `ThemeProvider` is instantiated once, but either will typecheck and lint cleanly.

