## Step 5 — `apps/web/src/components/ThemeSelector.tsx` (new)

Renders a row of clickable swatch cards. Each swatch is a mini editor mockup built from inline styles using the theme's color values (no Tailwind utilities for colors — these are dynamic JS values).

```typescript
import { useTheme, THEME_IDS, getTheme } from "../hooks/useTheme";

export function ThemeSelector() {
  const { themeId, setTheme } = useTheme();

  return (
    <div className="flex flex-wrap gap-3" role="radiogroup" aria-label="Theme">
