No new dependencies. No build config changes.

---

## Files to Create

| File | Purpose |
|---|---|
| `packages/shared/src/theme.ts` | Types + built-in theme definitions |
| `apps/web/src/components/ThemeProvider.tsx` | Module store + React Context + `useTheme` hook |
| `apps/web/src/components/ThemeSelector.tsx` | Swatch-based selector component |

## Files to Modify

| File | Change |
|---|---|
| `packages/shared/package.json` | Add `./theme` subpath export |
| `apps/web/src/hooks/useTheme.ts` | Replace with thin re-export shim |
| `apps/web/src/index.css` | Append three `[data-theme]` palette blocks |
