## Step 7 — `apps/web/src/routes/__root.tsx`

Add import:
```typescript
import { ThemeProvider } from "../components/ThemeProvider";
```

Restructure `RootRouteView` to a single return, wrapping both branches in one `<ThemeProvider>`:

```tsx
function RootRouteView() {
